<td bgcolor="#CECECE" class="btext" width="100%"><b>DoD Update News</b> - <span class=bsmall>posted by  <a class='nNewsMailLink' href='mailto:ice.m@btinternet.com'>ICE.M</a> on Thu 12 July 2001 20:05:55 | <a href="comments.php?section=1&index=261">Comments (0)</a></span></td>
