<tr>
<td bgcolor="#EEEEEE" colspan=2 class=news>
<table><tr><td valign=top><img src='images/icon_general.gif' alt='General News' border=0></td><td width="100%" valign=top><a href=http://www.dayofdefeatmod.com/  class=colourise target=_blank>Day of Defeat site</a> has been updated with news on what will feature in the up-and-coming Beta 1.3B patch that will be client-side. Don't worry, they report that it is currently around 4.39 MB, so that shouldn't take too long to download. It is currently in testing and more news should be released in a couple of days.<br><br><span class=quote>-Black Box around grenade smoke in software mode<br>-Sprites and water disapearing behind grenade/explosion smoke<br>-Bayonet TK's<br>-Grenade TK's<br>-Prone Cheat<br>-Box Cheat<br>-Updated Snowtown<br>-And other miscelanious things...</span></td></tr></table>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
