<td bgcolor="#EEEEEE" colspan=2 class=news>
<table><tr><td valign=top><img src='images/icon_general.gif' alt='General News' border=0></td><td width="100%" valign=top>As I was going through some news sites today, I noticed a post on <a href="http://www.bluesnews.com" class=colourise>Blue's News</a> where they quoted Guy Welsh's (him being a Sierra person) post on the Sierra Forums.<br><br><span class=quote>"Sierra and Valve have been busy testing the most recent update for Half-Life. This version will include a new update utility and Deathmatch Classic, as well as a host of fixes. <br><br>We're aiming to release the update sometime mid-morning on Wednesday, July 11th."</span><br><br>So there you have it. Be prepared to another 0.5k/sec download.</td></tr></table>
